# Frequently Asked Questions

## Why are credentials missing?

Credentials are intentionally excluded for security.

## Which OpenAI model is supported?

GPT-4.1 Mini

## Which Gmail account is supported?

Any Gmail account connected through OAuth.

## Can I use multiple RSS feeds?

Yes.

This is planned for Version 2.0.

## Can I publish directly to LinkedIn?

Planned for Version 3.0.
